{"type": "article", "id": 51263, "title": "用裁剪服装的方法设计家具，结果会是什么样？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-19T23:12:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 28788, "name": "失物招领"}, {"id": 48561, "name": "Tait"}, {"id": 39422, "name": "Formafantasma"}, {"id": 48562, "name": "Mario Zoller"}, {"id": 48563, "name": "Dingding Hu"}, {"id": 48564, "name": "Yiannis Ghikas"}, {"id": 41284, "name": "蔡烈超"}, {"id": 48565, "name": "Adam Cornish"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 125, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180319204828cHp3oWKRX7fevaGB.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Seam Chair by Adam Cornish for Tait</h3><p>Seam 是澳洲设计师 Adam Cornish 为本地制造商 Tait 设计的首款家具系列，目前正在墨尔本设计周上展出。设计师使用基于剪裁的工艺，制造出这些铝制座椅。根据设计师的说法，制造过程与如何将一块织物剪裁成合体服装的方式类似。</p><p>得到的结果就是整个系列看起来很统一，线条流畅，轮廓清晰，设计细节精致。</p><p>整个 Seam 系列包括餐椅、堆叠椅、吧台、餐桌以及咖啡桌。 Adam Cornish 表示，家具“丰富而朴实”的配色参考了澳洲海岸线、地形和植物的特征，比如深海蓝、白千层属植物的颜色、赭石色、苍白桉树的颜色以及林地灰色等等。</p><p>每把椅子的主体以及桌面均由铝制成。由于其高弹性，重量轻，强度高和耐腐蚀性，同样适用于户外。除了不锈钢或铝外，腿部还有木材选择，让金属家具更显温暖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319204905cOnKT0vQ453rlRfG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319204906F4csHjueYt7GKrQa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319204906lK4C3yI9UxJhYDTo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018031920490849EK325xXVSCPY6m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319204908FlLn0KyMGOw48pua.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319204908IxEMFUGkqpQwnZOu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319204908QNrqL9XGbyAx86OC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/03/19/adam-cornish-seam-furniture-melbourne-design-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cuddle Chair by 蔡烈超 for 失物招领</h3><p>十年前，原创家居设计品牌失物招领推出了曾在 1940-50 年代风靡一时的铁管椅，保留原始结构，更换上舒适的软包面料，加厚了坐垫，并调节了椅背角度。这也成了失物招领的代表作之一。</p><p>最近，他们邀请设计师蔡烈超一起，推出更新版本的铁管椅，圆润又轻盈，“就像一个踏实温暖的怀抱”。除了青苔绿，还有珊瑚粉这样温柔的颜色。</p><p>这把椅子，兼具古典与精致，设计师抓住了铁管椅最具特点的部分。它强化了之前“天津铁管椅”扶手与腿部连接的结构关系，去掉了木扶手，腿部仍然是优雅的人字造型，整体造型却更为轻快，更具现代感。售价 2300 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-c-s.w4002-15265269258.45.245140eedFoxf5&amp;id=566288879735\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319210820TuZvn39DSpV6A7tR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319210820PYQkIy54SuhdtHOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319210821lkc3a0zWLE1nw548.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319210820ptaYqze1G84lcdnU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675168\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Torus by Yiannis Ghikas</h3><p>雅典设计师 Yiannis Ghikas 最近推出了一款摩登气息浓烈的不锈钢葡萄酒冰桶 Torus。这个名字，来源于冰桶独特的圆环形提手，巧妙地围合出冰桶本身优雅的线条。</p><p>“在葡萄酒饮酒历史中，品酒服务一直起到强调社会阶级差异的作用，但同时也是尊重、爱与关怀的表达，” Yiannis Ghikas 表示。在设计过程中，设计师试图以象征方式赋予侍者荣誉感，让他们成为此次设计的着眼点，为他们提供 360 度的提手。</p><p>Torus 分为磨砂款、亮面款以及拉丝款，均为不锈钢材质制作而成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319210906kVRSHo4uKbzawPph.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319210906qsLy6jJFkhKtIeD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319210906Q3iuOvC7lwmFMcoL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803192109071q3OR9fE80zVwotC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319210907Z4xzQtJT9ngRLfkP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319210909X7N3dcg61maqV5nH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/torus-wine-bucket-yiannis-ghikas-03-16-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Chinatown Walk Signage Collection by Dingding Hu</h3><p>Dingding Hu 是一位来自纽约的插画师，她迷恋色彩，也擅于观察生活。最近，她与纽约市交通局艺术部门、美国中国博物馆合作，在曼哈顿唐人街制作了 45 款作品，在街上作为引导标识，目前正在曼哈顿下区的街道上展示。</p><p>根据 Google 地图的“Quick Facts”，唐人街是一个人口密集的地方，吸引了很多吃货与游客慕名来到这里，品尝很多中国与东南亚餐馆的饺子、猪油包和手工面条。这套插画作品试图提醒游客们，唐人街不仅是一个能够喝到美味珍珠奶茶的地方，这里的街道也有着丰富的游戏、庆典、音乐等等。更多插图作品，请点击这里<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/59743983/Chinatown-Walk-Signage-Collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">查阅她的 Benhance 个人主页</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211116dwgzJkQD3a7H2OlS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211118517BxHnT6VloWkfv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211120ouEm6PfHsyKqDIY8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211121CRtFNl24Q9IGhuZ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803192111245cG4BoVRHaQps9hM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211124ocwaBRT8KHu05qSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211129IEFZyLP7n1ch2Hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/59743983/Chinatown-Walk-Signage-Collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>MA.ZO Copy Mirror by Mario Zoller</h3><p>在苏黎世工业、平面设计师 Mario Zoller 看来，镜子是个独特的物体，它是少有的能够为我们自己提供副本的物体，充实我们的自我认知。基于这个概念，它设计了一款名为 <a href=\"https://mariozoller.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MA.ZO</a> 的复制镜，这是他自己名字的缩写。</p><p>这面镜子造型极简，为的是将镜像和观察者至于焦点位置，避免分散注意力。两条平行的优雅的木条框架就是全部装饰了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803192112264KgQ30XnE6kFi7xJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211227TBmjpfsiRZoKbtq8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803192112274rA29ZOPtgCYhl80.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211227Pkt7VvWNZmazFeL8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211227l7Cu52gcUL3Qivoq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://mariozoller.ch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mario Zoller</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Helmet Lamp by Formafantasma</h3><p>三块精细抛光的镀金黄铜板，做成的这款头盔灯，形成的内部夹角区域藏有一个 LED 光源，提供照明的同时，更具有雕塑般的观感。据说设计师的灵感是在参观了罗马古城遗址后得来的。</p><p>用户看得到的，只是弯曲的黄铜板和带电的底座，开关被隐藏起来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211303SubQaIeTVKBCp0Ji.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211303XkajcyY9QUMr4IAZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211303jglFEPUCo9WDxJRM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211303Vuo6YzGFlZicrUbO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180319211309o8HfdBjK9cQWlgR4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.formafantasma.com/Helmet\" rel=\"nofollow\">Formafantasma</a></p>"}